title: Euro 2016 Qualifiers: Vincent Kompany to miss Belgium's match against Andorra
text: Vincent Kompany will miss Belgium's Euro 2016 qualifier in Andorra on Saturday with a calf injury but will train on his own over the next few days in agreement with Manchester City, the country's soccer officials said on Wednesday. Â»
